    "body": "> If done properly, we should be able to create a Theme by simply defining a theme file with just color variables.\r\nGeneric and component variables should be derived from that.\r\n\r\nYeah this is a great idea. It was the goal when I first started the theme, but like you said, with the addition of more and more specific components, it ended up getting hard to do that, especially since at the start, colors weren't as well named as Simon did now.\r\n\r\nAnyway, I'm all for it, it does need a nice cleanup.",
